<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<bug>
	<id>4110</id>
	<title>Post List: Add link to publish draft post directly from post list</title>
	<description>
		<paragraph id="1">
			<sentence id="1.1">### Expected behavior</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="2">
			<sentence id="2.1">When viewing drafts in the post list, I expect to see the options to Edit, Preview, Publish, and Trash the post.</sentence>
			<sentence id="2.2">Here are those options in Calypso:</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="3">
			<sentence id="3.1">!</sentence>
			<sentence id="3.2">[screen shot 2016-05-20 at 12 35 57 pm](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/8658164/15426609/6c9f8de2-1e87-11e6-8d9d-9696b34a55d8.png)</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="4">
			<sentence id="4.1">Those options are also available in WPiOS:</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="5">
			<sentence id="5.1">!</sentence>
			<sentence id="5.2">[screen shot 2016-05-20 at 12 39 27 pm](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/8658164/15426691/ead7dac0-1e87-11e6-84a0-be8a045f41a3.png)</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="6">
			<sentence id="6.1">### Actual behavior</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="7">
			<sentence id="7.1">Drafts only have the options to Edit, View/Preview, or Trash/Delete.</sentence>
			<sentence id="7.2">There is no option to publish directly from the post list:</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="8">
			<sentence id="8.1">!</sentence>
			<sentence id="8.2">[2016-05-20 11 41 13](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/8658164/15426745/69c62238-1e88-11e6-92c3-689ca257d114.png)</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="9">
			<sentence id="9.1">### Steps to reproduce the behavior</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="10">
			<sentence id="10.1">1 Open the WordPress app</sentence>
			<sentence id="10.2">2 Create a new post in the editor</sentence>
			<sentence id="10.3">3 Save the new post as a draft</sentence>
			<sentence id="10.4">4 Open the Blog Posts list</sentence>
			<sentence id="10.5">5 Find the draft post in the list of posts</sentence>
		</paragraph>
		<paragraph id="11">
			<sentence id="11.1">##### Tested on Nexus 9, Android 6.0.1, WPAndroid alpha-8
Also reported by a user in an app review (WPAndroid 5.3)</sentence>
		</paragraph>
	</description>
</bug>
